headline.main: Marsh and Renshaw Hit Fifties to Give Australia Lead
headline.print_headline: Marsh and Renshaw Hit Fifties to Give Australia Lead

lead_paragraph: Shaun Marsh and Matt Renshaw struck contrasting half-centuries on an engrossing day of cricket to help Australia take a first-innings lead of 48 against India in the second test at the M. Chinnaswamy Stadium on Sunday.
